      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior paint is entirely original and flawless, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the interior remains in pristine state with no signs of wear on the leather or trim. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history documenting its care. A truly exceptional example for a collector or discerning buyer who expects nothing less than perfection.",
